---
title: Cal Smart Chipotle Beef Burrito Bowls with Guacamole and Pickled Jalapeños
description: This bowl packs in all the flavours of a burrito: Mexican-style rice, charred veggies, zippy guac, spicy pickled jalapeños and garlicky, smoky beef! No tortilla? No problem!
